definitions.definition: A game played on a rectangular court between two teams of two to six players which involves striking a ball back and forth over a net .
The inflated ball used in such a game.

main_definition: ( uncountable ) A game played on a rectangular court between two teams of two to six players which involves striking a ball back and forth over a net .
secondary_definitions: ( countable ) The inflated ball used in such a game.
